      "content": "thanks, i tried that margin fix but it didnt really solve it. the elements are still clashing and looks like they are literally sitting on top of each other on some devices. it feels like the layout is just being \"pushed\" out of place randomly. \n\ncould it be a z-index issue or is there something else in the flex behavior that would make them stack like that? i'm also seeing some weird gaps in the padding for no reason.",
